text: Wely is a village in the Dutch province of Gelderland. It is a part of the municipality of Neder-Betuwe, and lies about 8 km south of Wageningen. The statistical area "Wely", which also can include the surrounding countryside, has a population of around 180.Statistics Netherlands (CBS), Statline: Kerncijfers wijken en buurten 2003-2005.
